Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.34,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,{Wh-What was that sudden gust?}C-Cái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:29.10,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,{Gosh, that really startled me...}Thiệt tình...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:34.85,Main,Man,0,0,0,,{Is it just me, or did it feel more like\N }{\i1}{something}{\i0}{ blew by rather than just wind?}Hình như vừa rồi không chỉ là một cơn gió...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:38.33,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Hey, didn't we just pass some humans?}Này này, chúng ta vừa vượt qua hai người thì phải?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:39.74,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Never you mind.}Kệ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.23,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{There's no way they saw us.}Bọn họ không thấy được đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.40,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Focus more on moving faster, Hayato.}Tập trung tăng tốc đi, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:47.78,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{D-Damn it! Get back here!}C-Chết tiệt! Chờ đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:50.41,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{You hag in a kid's body!}Bà già trong lốt loli chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.78,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Nine hours for a lap around the earth...}Đi hết một vòng trái đất mất 9 tiếng à...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:18.70,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{That's much slower than you usually manage.}Chậm hơn mọi khi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:19.98,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Are you slacking?}Không nghiêm túc à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:24.44,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Did you forget the part where you beat \Nthe shit out of me, you senile old bitch?!}Bà quên cái phần đánh chết tôi\N trên đường đi rồi à, mụ già chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.11,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{What arrogance when you're still half-baked.}Thiệt tình, cái mồm lúc nào cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:32.41,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Do you think that'll help \Nyou become a proper Idaten?}Ngươi nghĩ chỉ nhiêu đó đã có thể\N trở thành Idaten hoàn hảo à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:35.36,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{What exactly is a "proper" \NIdaten supposed to be anyway?}Idaten hoàn hảo là gì chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.66,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{How does being fast even matter?}Chạy nhanh hơn nữa để làm gì chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:42.41,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{You drag me out here every day, \Nwork me to the bone... And for what?}Ngày nào cũng lôi tôi ra đây, \Nluyện tập chết đi sống lại... để làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:51.37,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{In the old days, endless hordes \Nof monsters ran rampant across the land.}Ngày xưa, hành tinh này tràn ngập quái vật.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:54.74,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{We are deities called forth to do battle.}Chúng ta là những vị thần chiến đấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:58.02,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{We used our speed to fight, and—}Sử dụng tốc độ để chiến đấu và--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:05:00.36,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Yeah, yeah, I've heard this story.}Rồi rồi, nghe mãi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:04.33,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{But it's been eighty years since \NI popped up in this world.}Nhưng tôi chỉ mới xuất hiện ở đây được 80 năm thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.28,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{And when were these monsters sealed away?}Và lũ ác quỷ bị phong ấn khi nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.90,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{About 800 years ago.}800 năm trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:12.90,Main,Hayto,0,0,0,,{See? So when's this seal busting open?}Đấy. Thế khi nào nó mới phá được phong ấn?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.66,Main,Hayto,0,0,0,,{The world looks peaceful enough to me.}Thế giới đã trở nên hòa bình rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:17.20,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Where are you going?}Ngươi định đi đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:20.88,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{To have some fun. \NI've hit my training quota for the day.}Tìm niềm vui. Hôm nay luyện tập thế đủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.50,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{What's the problem?}Có vấn đề gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:32.14,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Grandfather, it seems like 800 \Nyears of peace was too long...}Ông à, có vẻ 800 năm hòa bình là quá dài...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:41.81,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Hey, sorry about the holdup, Ysley.}Chào, chờ lâu không Ysley.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.06,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{You're as swift as ever, Hayato.}Vẫn nhanh như mọi khi nhỉ, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:48.43,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Not as swift as old Rin, though...}Vẫn chưa bằng bà già Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:50.19,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Well, she's a freak of nature.}Bà ta là quái vật rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:52.74,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{I'll still outdo her one day.}Nhất định tớ sẽ vượt qua bà ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:58.29,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{All you ever do is read those human books. \NWould it kill you to train a little?}Cậu chỉ toàn ngồi đọc sách của nhân loại nhỉ? \NSao không tham gia huấn luyện?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:02.00,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I'd really rather not. I'd die.}Tha tớ đi, chết mất...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.75,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Besides...}Với cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.04,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I love studying.}Tớ thích học.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:11.51,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{And I'm able to learn more than \Nany human can in their limited lifespan.}Và tớ có thể học hỏi nhiều\N hơn bất cứ nhân loại nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:15.76,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Since the world's at peace, what's the \Nharm in having an Idaten like that?}Dù gì thế giới cũng hòa bình mà,\N người ta cần gì đến Idaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:19.29,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Hey, I'm not the old bag, \Nso I've got no problem with it.}Tớ không phải bà già kia nên không ý kiến gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:22.25,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Come on. Let's go see what Paula's doing.}Đi thôi. Xem Paula đang làm gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:42.41,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Jeez, couldn't you guys be a little quieter?\N You scared them all away!}Thiệt tình, mấy cậu im lặng một chút đi. \NChúng sợ quá bay hết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:46.67,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{We're not you. We can't run \Nlike dainty princesses.}Bọn này khác cậu, không dịu dàng\N như công chúa được đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:50.60,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Did the birds tell you anything interesting?}Mấy con chim có nói gì thú vị không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:52.88,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it,}Nghĩ lại thì,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:56.73,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{they said there's a bunch of humans \Ngathering by the glaciers up north.}chúng nói có cả đống người đang\N tập trung ở sông băng phía Bắc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:59.24,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{What the hell are the humans doing there?}Con người làm gì ở đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:01.18,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{How am I supposed to know?}Sao tớ biết?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:04.12,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{They mentioned giant green birds, too.}Chúng nói thấy một con chim to màu xanh nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.60,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{But those are probably airplanes.}Có vẻ là máy bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:10.19,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Sounds like a military transport\N for the Zoble Empire.}Là máy bay vận chuyển của đế quốc Zoble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:11.98,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{When you say Zoble...}Zoble á...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.98,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{You mean the weaponized industrial country}Cái đất nước quân sự hóa quá đà
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:16.88,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{whose air and water have gone to shit?}khiến không khí và nguồn nước ô nhiễm nặng?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:18.98,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{What does their military \Nwant in a glacial region?}Chúng muốn gì ở khu vực băng giá này?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:19.91,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{No clue.}Không biết nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.99,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{It'll be faster to go see \Nthan stand around and guess.}Thay vì ngồi đoán mò thì đến coi thử.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:26.88,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{It's only 400 kilometers away. \NEven you two can make that in 20 minutes.}Cũng tầm 400km thôi chứ mấy.\N Cỡ hai cậu chắc tầm 20 phút.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.15,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I guess we should get going.}Chắc tớ cũng đi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.15,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{You're right.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.95,Italics,Hayato,0,0,0,,{That sure is a lot of humans...}Đúng là đông người thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.37,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.15,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{How are things looking?}Thế nào rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.44,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Hey, you made it.}Đến rồi à.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:56.78,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{I dunno what they're after, \Nbut that's a hell of a lot of security.}Không biết chúng làm gì nhưng cả đống cảnh vệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:59.46,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Whatever they want is probably over there,}Có vẻ chúng muốn gì đó dưới kia,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:03.04,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{but with this many people, \NI can't get closer without them noticing.}nhưng đông người quá nên khó tiếp cận lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.49,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Then could you check it out, Paula?}Vậy thì cậu thử đến đó xem, Paula?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:06.75,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Me?}Tớ á?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.22,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Put this in when you go.}Mang theo thứ này.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:20.17,Main,Captain,0,0,0,,{Something the matter, Dr. Obami?}Có chuyện gì sao, tiến sĩ Obami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:22.26,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{No, I must've imagined it.}Không, do ta tưởng tượng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:24.67,Main,Captain,0,0,0,,{How is the thawing proceeding?}Quá trình tan băng sao rồi ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:28.77,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{It's 98 percent complete! Basically finished.}98% rồi, chắc sắp xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:32.48,Italics,Obami,0,0,0,,{He'll be ready to move out \Nas soon as he's awake.}Nó đã sẵn sàng hoạt động khi thức tỉnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:43.24,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Wh-What is this thing?}C-Cái gì kia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:47.25,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{One of the demons who left a blazing \Ntrail of carnage 800 years ago,}Một trong những ác quỷ đã để lại\N cuộc tàn sát 800 năm trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:52.16,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{and with a little elbow grease, he's still \Nfully capable of destroying the world...}Đến tận bây giờ, chỉ cần nghiêm túc \Nthì nó vẫn có thể phá hủy cả thế giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.42,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Gyudo-kun the demon beast!}Ma thú Gyudo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:09:00.43,Italics,Obami,0,0,0,,{A bottom feeder as far as demons go, \Nbut more than a match for any human military.}Tuy trong ác quỷ thì nó không mạnh mấy nhưng\N cũng dư sức thổi bay quân đội nhân loại.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.48,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{What do you think? Is that cool, or what?}Ngươi thấy sao? Tuyệt không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:08.20,Main,Captain,0,0,0,,{And with that power under our control, \NHotaena and Sarabael will be easy targets?}Và nếu có thể kiểm soát được sức mạnh đó,\N Hotaena và Sarabael sẽ nằm trong tầm tay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:11.44,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Humans were never a consideration \Nin the first place.}Ngay từ đầu nhân loại đã chẳng có cửa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:16.27,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{The question is how the gods\N may have changed...}Vấn đề là thần linh sẽ thế nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.38,Main,Captain,0,0,0,,{Gods?}Thần linh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.14,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Don't you worry about it!}Đừng có lo lắng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:21.28,Main,Captain,0,0,0,,{Right...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:24.18,Italics,Captain,0,0,0,,{This old timer's as strange as ever.}Lão ta vẫn kì lạ như mọi khi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:27.91,Italics,Captain,0,0,0,,{And how is he not cold, dressed like that?}Cơ mà không lạnh à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:33.11,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{So this is one of those demons that\Nthe old bag never shuts up about...}Đây là lũ ác quỷ mà bà già hay nói à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.90,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{This was the worth the trip!}Chẳng bõ công mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.68,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't be so pleased if I were you.}Không phải chuyện vui đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:42.16,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Why not? It's just one leftover small fry.}Sao không? Chỉ còn mỗi một con thôi chứ mấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:46.72,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Well, I'm sure Rin-san could defeat \Nit in the worst case scenario...}Tệ nhất thì Rin-san sẽ đánh bại nó...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:51.66,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{But how does this Dr. Obami \Nknow about 800 years ago?}Nhưng tại sao tiến sĩ Obami này\N lại biết mấy chuyện 800 năm trước?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:54.23,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{About us or the name of this demon?}Về chúng ta và tên con quỷ đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:58.23,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{There shouldn't be any humans left \Nwith that kind of knowledge...}Đáng ra con người phải không biết đến nó chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:02.24,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Maybe he's been kicking \Nfor 800 years like Granny.}Có thể lão ta cũng như bà già kia, sống 800 năm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:06.24,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{I mean, not that any human's capable of that.}Cơ mà chẳng nhân loại nào sống được vậy đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:08.35,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{It's true no human is capable of that...}Đúng là nhân loại thì không thể...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:12.25,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{But what if this doctor isn't human?}Nhưng nếu lão ta không phải con người?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:15.25,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{What if he's a surviving demon}Nếu lão là một con quỷ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:17.38,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{who's been working for eight centuries}đã sống sót suốt 800 năm qua
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:21.21,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{toward the revival of demonkind?}để hồi sinh ác quỷ thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:38.34,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Hell, yeah! Free after 800 years!}Quá đã! Tự do sau 800 năm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:44.10,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Hip hip hooray! \NHip hip hooray! Hip hip hooray!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:43.46,Main,Captain,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Doctor! Is it safe to be standing here?}Tiến sĩ, nó ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:47.56,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Don't you worry. Gyudo-kun is \Npretty docile, generally speaking.}Đừng lo, Gyudo-kun rất ngoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:50.18,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{As long as you don't provoke him, \Nhe won't attack.}Miễn đừng khiêu khích nó là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:54.62,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Though that doesn't apply to gods...}Dù điều đó không áp dụng cho các vị thần...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:00.52,Main,Captain,0,0,0,,{Doctor! What is this?!}Tiến sĩ? Vậy là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:04.42,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Could the accelerated thawing \Nhave driven him mad?}Tan băng nhanh quá khiến não nó bị chập à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:21.11,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,Paula!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:24.40,Main,Captain,0,0,0,,{Enough! Fire at will!}Đủ rồi! Tất cả bắn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:31.91,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Stop that, you fool!\N He'll come after us next!}Dừng lại lũ ngu! Nó sẽ nhắm vào chúng ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:41.01,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Damn it... What's gotten into him?}Chết tiệt... Rốt cuộc là chuyện gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:45.55,Italics,Obami,0,0,0,,{A girl?}Một cô gái?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:02.02,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Wow!}Ồ!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:11.34,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Huh, I let him have with that kick, \Nbut he seems to be fine.}Ăn một đá mà vẫn khỏe thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.97,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{You can run if you want, y'know.}Cậu có thể chạy tùy thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:17.79,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{And that's exactly what I'll do\N if I think we can't beat him.}Ờ, và cậu cũng nên chạy khi đánh không lại nó đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:20.51,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{I'm sure of it! They must be Idaten!}Không thể nhầm được! Là Idaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:22.87,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{This is the perfect opportunity...}Cơ hội hoàn hảo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:28.77,Italics,Obami,0,0,0,,{A generation of Idaten softened \Nby the comfort of peacetime...}Một thế hệ Idaten trở nên mềm yếu vì hòa bình quá lâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:32.64,Italics,Obami,0,0,0,,{This should be good. \NLet's see what you can manage.}Quá tốt. Hãy cho ta thấy các ngươi có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:39.81,Main,Captain,0,0,0,,{Who are you boys? Where did you come from?!}Đám nhóc này là ai?  Các ngươi đến từ đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:44.02,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Your odds are better staying buried \Nand fighting the cold, pops.}Tốt hơn là ông nên nằm yên đó\N và làm ấm người đi, lão già.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.17,Main,Captain,0,0,0,,{You little...}Thằng nhãi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.07,Main,Captain,0,0,0,,{Who do you think you're talking to?!}Mày nghĩ đang nói chuyện với ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.29,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Ow! Hey!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:53.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{Why you...}Ông...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:56.96,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{The hell was that for, asshole?! That hurt!}Làm cái gì thế hả? Đau biết không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.10,Main,Captain,0,0,0,,{What the—?!}Cái quái--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:12:59.50,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Uh, behind you!}Phía sau cậu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:04.79,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:11.51,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{He's probably dead.}Nó chết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:18.47,Italics,Obami,0,0,0,,{An attack at the speed of sound \Nthat can generate a sonic boom?}Một đòn tấn công âm thanh tạo ra vụ nổ sóng âm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:22.39,Italics,Obami,0,0,0,,{That'd be enough to demolish a tank, but...}Nó đủ để phá hủy một chiếc xe tăng, nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:26.36,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:35.22,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{It's not enough to hurt Gyudo-kun.}Chỉ thế không đủ làm Gyudo-kun bị thương đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.28,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{That makes two.}Vậy là xong hai đứa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:45.37,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{And we're done.}Và kết thúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:48.38,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{I must say, peace does nothing\N for resilience...}Hòa bình không thể giúp chúng ta mạnh mẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.62,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{What?! Impossible!}Cái quái? Không thể nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:06.60,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{His heart was gouged out!}Nội tạng bị thổi bay rồi mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.23,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{He's not very fast.}Nó không nhanh lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:15.69,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{If we focus on evasion, \Nwe should easily be able to escape.}Nếu chúng ta trốn sẽ thoát được nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:21.24,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{It's like he's only attacking \NIdaten on instinct.}Cứ như nó chỉ tập trung tấn công Idaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:25.96,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Lashing out at us, before anything else,\N after being thawed out...}Vừa tan băng đã tấn công bắn phá bọn mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:29.00,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{That suggests the cognitive \Ncapacity of an insect.}Khác gì một con côn trùng đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:32.01,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{What's going on here?!}Rốt cuộc chuyện này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:37.60,Italics,Obami,0,0,0,,{Was it some kind of trick? Or is piercing \Ntheir hearts not enough to kill them?!}Một cú lừa? Hay phá hủy nội tạng không thể giết chúng?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:40.92,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,Ysley?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.11,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{You're awake?}Cậu tỉnh rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.40,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Whoa, you're injured! Are you okay?!}Cậu bị thương nặng vậy? Ổn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:48.50,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{It does hurt pretty badly, \Nso can you stand on your own?}Khá là đau nên là cậu tự đứng lên nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.84,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{It only hurts? You're not gonna die?}Chỉ đau thôi á? Cậu không chết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:54.86,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{You'll understand if you ever \Nget your heart gouged out.}Cậu sẽ hiểu nếu thử moi hết nội tạng ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:58.32,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{More importantly, this exchange \Nhas made three things clear.}Cơ mà tớ đã biết được 3 điều.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:03.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{First, that monster is incredibly \Ntough and powerful,}Đầu tiên, con quỷ đó cực kì mạnh mẽ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:06.64,Main,First,0,0,0,,{but it can't compare to us \NIdaten in terms of speed.}Nhưng so về tốc độ thì thua xa Idaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:08.67,Main,First,0,0,0,,{If we need to flee, \Nthat shouldn't be a problem.}Nếu chạy trốn khỏi nó thì quá dễ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:10.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{Second...}Thứ hai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:15.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{It seems the good doctor \Ndoesn't know much about us,}Có vẻ lão tiến sĩ không biết nhiều về chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:19.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{considering how surprised he was that \NI survived having my heart pierced...}Lão ta đã ngạc nhiên khi thấy tớ vẫn chưa chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:21.99,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{That surprised me, too!}Tớ cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:24.64,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I suppose it would.}Cậu không biết cũng phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:27.31,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{To be honest, the first time\N I had my heart pulped}Nói thật, lần đầu nội tạng tớ bị thổi bay
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:30.50,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{and my neck broken, \NI thought I was a goner, too...}và cổ thì gãy nát, cứ tưởng chết rồi chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:38.24,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{What's this? An earthquake?}Gì thế? Động đất à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:43.49,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{As for the third thing,\N that monster is strong.}Và thứ 3, con quỷ này rất mạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.20,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{However...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:51.33,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{You think I'm gonna let that slide, \Nyou piece of shit?!}Mày dám làm thế với tao à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.46,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Hope you're ready for payback a millionfold!}Tao sẽ bắt mày trả lại gấp trăm lần!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:57.12,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Hayato, who has been training \Nwith Rin-san for 80 years,}Hayato, được Rin-san huấn luyện suốt 80 năm,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.76,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{should have no problem fighting him.}nó không phải đối thủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:01.48,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Eat this!}Nhận lấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:11.87,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Hey.}Này.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:17.03,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{You left your body wide open,\N you beefy dumbass!}Mày hơi sơ hở rồi đấy, đồ ngu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.21,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Nice! Get him, Hayato!}Ngon! Xử nó đi, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.92,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{He's nothing like the one in glasses.}Nó khác hẳn thằng nhóc đeo kính.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:41.69,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{This doesn't look good...}Không ổn rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:07.42,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Okay! On your feet, big boy!}Rồi! Đứng lên đi, bé bự!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.58,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{This time, I'm blowing your head clean off—}Lần này tao sẽ thổi bay đầu mày--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:14.98,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{What? Is he dead?}Hả? Chết rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:23.59,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{He }{\i0}{is}{\i1}{ dead...}Nó đã chết...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:29.35,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Immediate death following destructive \Norgan trauma is a trait of organisms.}Chết ngay sau khi bị phá hủy nội tạng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:33.85,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Meaning demons are closer \Nto living creatures than us Idaten...}Vậy là lũ ác quỷ giống với sinh vật sống hơn Idaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:40.23,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{I wasn't able to retrieve Gyudo-kun,}Tuy thất bại trong việc hồi sinh Gyudo-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:43.82,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{but I've obtained data that more \Nthan makes up for that loss.}nhưng ta đã có được những thông tin quý giá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:46.57,Italics,Obami,0,0,0,,{Now, you'll have to excuse \Nme as I make my exit.}Giờ thì xin thứ lỗi nhưng ta xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:50.51,Italics,Obami,0,0,0,,{Farewell to you, new generation of Idaten!}Một ngày tốt lành, thế hệ Idaten mới!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:53.41,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{That's...}Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:55.22,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{the new high-speed VTOL fighter jet}mẫu máy bay chiến đấu mới nhất VTOL,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.73,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{that can maintain a cruising speed of Mach 2!}có thể duy trì tốc độ Mach 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.67,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Although, that said...}Cơ mà chỉ thế thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:04.09,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Wh-What... What was that?}C-Cái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:04.80,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Yo.}Chào.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:06.09,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Yo, }{\i1}{what}{\i0}{?!}Chào? Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:09.10,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{It can't escape Hayato.}Nó sẽ không thoát khỏi Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:12.18,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{All right, Gramps, quit panicking.}Thôi nào lão già, đừng hốt hoảng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:14.56,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Let's land this thing and have a little chat.}Chúng ta nói chuyện chút đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.19,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Here we go...}Nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:18.69,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{S-Stop! Don't do anything drastic!}D-Dừng lại! Đừng làm gì nguy hiểm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:28.06,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Wait, humans die from falls, right?}Cơ mà con người sẽ chết nếu rơi xuống nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:31.08,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Did I do that wrong?}Mình làm gì sai thì phải?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:35.91,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Hey, Gramps?}Này ông già?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:37.57,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{You still alive?}Còn sống không?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:46.80,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Say, Ysley, how long are you \Ngoing to study that dead monster?}Nè Ysley, cậu còn nghiên cứu con quỷ đó đến khi nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:50.08,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Huh? Ysley?}Ủa? Ysley?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.95,0:18:53.06,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{The monster's body is gone, too...}Cái xác cũng biến mất rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:56.67,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Yes, that's right. A dead monster specimen.}Phải. Một vật mẫu xác ác quỷ đã chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.81,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Retrieve it as quickly as possible, please.}Mau đến thu hồi ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.63,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{It's near where we first found it.}Nó gần với chỗ chúng ta tìm ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:04.78,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I'll send the specific \Ncoordinates in a moment.}Tôi sẽ gửi tọa độ cụ thể.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:07.03,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Listen, you need to hurry.}Nhanh lên nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:10.03,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Don't let Zoble get it first.}Đừng để Zoble nẫng tay trên.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:15.04,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Damn you, boy...}Thằng nhóc chết tiệt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.04,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{I can't believe you wrecked it!}Không thể tin ngươi lại phá hủy nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:20.16,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Do you realize how much of a pain\N it is to fix these bodies?!}Ngươi có biết tốn bao nhiêu để sửa lại cơ thể này không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:25.27,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{\an8}{You doof! Dunce! Dumb-dumb! \NStupid, stupid stupidhead!}Đồ ngốc! Ngu! Ranh con! Não không khí!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:24.12,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{So you're a robot, Gramps?}Ông là robot à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:29.68,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Man, Ysley is gonna have a lot \Nof fun taking you apart.}Vậy thì Ysley sẽ rất vui khi nghiên cứu ông đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:27.54,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Big old stupid stupidhead!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.95,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{You think this is a game, boy?!}Ngươi nghĩ đây là trò chơi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:35.82,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Try this on for size! The device all men \Ndream about making use of...}Nhận lấy! Thiết bị mà tất cả mọi người đều mơ ước...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:37.94,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\frz-12\fax-.05\fnArial\bord0\pos(368.572,45.714)\fs20\b1\c&H2B2D23&\4c&H594E51&\shad1\3c&H242819&}{Self-Destruct}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.00,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{A self-destruct switch!}Công tắc tự hủy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:37.94,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{And a-boop!}Và nhấn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.65,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Damn, guess he's a goner...}Lão già chết tiệt...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:07.42,Main,Troop A,0,0,0,,{Well, we're in for a treat.}Ồ, bữa tối ngon lành.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:09.22,Main,Troop B,0,0,0,,{She sure doesn't look like an old lady...}Không phải bà già...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:12.52,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{What are you men thinking?!}Các người đang nghĩ gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:16.75,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{You must realize God will not \Nforgive this kind of pillaging!}Các người nghĩ Thần linh \Nsẽ tha thứ cho hành động này sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:21.02,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{When the world was on the \Nverge of destruction,}Khi thế giới đang ở bờ vực diệt vong,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:23.25,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{God the creator descended from Heaven}Đấng sáng thế sẽ giáng trần,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:26.19,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{and brought salvation to \Nthe world and its people!}và mang sự cứu rỗi cho thế giới!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:31.06,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{What you're doing is blasphemy \Nin the eyes of our merciful—}Các người chỉ đang báng bổ thần linh--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.90,Main,Troop A,0,0,0,,{God? What's that?}Thần linh? Là cái quái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.54,Main,Troop C,0,0,0,,{Tissues work better than \Nblessings for sneezes!}Tao có khăn giấy đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:42.28,Main,Troop B,0,0,0,,{They've got other uses, too...}Giờ sẽ dùng rất nhiều đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:44.67,Main,Troop A,0,0,0,,{Well, God, we're gonna help ourselves.}Cảm ơn thần vì bữa ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:46.02,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{O Lord...}Thần linh ơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:16.41,Italics,Gill,0,0,0,,{Dear Lord, please...}Làm ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:21.30,Italics,Gill,0,0,0,,{Please... grant us salvation...}Hãy cứu rỗi chúng con...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:23.49,Italics,Gill,0,0,0,,{God!}Thần linh...
